title: A full DAO walk through
body: I propose that Patrick make a full and thorough end-to-end video about DAO's vs having to get a new tattoo.  If he would make a full-stack DAO walkthrough then he wouldn't have to get a new tattoo and all debts would be settled!
author: 0x54e160eD3a2cED1F797Bd239aF3Ee9BC285F6799
